[
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"0464\" class=\"\">Eliphaz</st> the <st data-num=\"08489\" class=\"\">Temanite</st> <st data-num=\"06030 0559\">answered</st>: </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cIs it to <st data-num=\"0410\" class=\"\">God</st> that a <st data-num=\"01397\" class=\"\">strong man</st> <st data-num=\"05532\" class=\"\">is of benefit</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Is it <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to</st> him <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> even a <st data-num=\"07919\" class=\"\">wise man</st> <st data-num=\"05532\" class=\"\">is profitable</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Is it <st data-num=\"02656\" class=\"\">of any special benefit</st><n id=\"1\" /> to the <st data-num=\"07706\" class=\"\">Almighty</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> you should <st data-num=\"06663\" class=\"\">be righteous</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">or <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">is</st> it any <st data-num=\"01215\" class=\"\">gain</st> to him<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> you <st data-num=\"08552\" class=\"\">make</st> your <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">ways</st> <st data-num=\"08552\" class=\"\">blameless</st>?<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Is it because of your <st data-num=\"03374\" class=\"\">piety</st><n id=\"1\" /> that he <st data-num=\"03198\" class=\"\">rebukes</st> you<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">goes</st> to <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">judgment</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> you?<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Is <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> your <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">wickedness</st> <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">great</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">is</st> there <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"07093\" class=\"\">end</st> to your <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">iniquity</st>? </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetrybreak\">\u201c<st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> you <st data-num=\"02254\" class=\"\">took pledges</st><n id=\"1\" /> from your <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">brothers</st> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02600\" class=\"\">for no reason</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and you <st data-num=\"06584\" class=\"\">stripped</st> the <st data-num=\"0899\" class=\"\">clothing</st> from the <st data-num=\"06174\" class=\"\">naked</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">You <st data-num=\"08248\" class=\"\">gave</st> the <st data-num=\"05889\" class=\"\">weary</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st> <st data-num=\"08248\" class=\"\">to drink</st><p class=\"poetry\">and from the <st data-num=\"07456\" class=\"\">hungry</st> you <st data-num=\"04513\" class=\"\">withheld</st> <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">food</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Although you were a <st data-num=\"02220\" class=\"\">powerful</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> owning <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">an <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">honored</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">man</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">living</st> on it,<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">you <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> <st data-num=\"0490\" class=\"\">widows</st> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">away</st> <st data-num=\"07387\" class=\"\">empty-handed</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"02220\" class=\"\">arms</st><n id=\"1\" /> of the <st data-num=\"03490\" class=\"\">orphans</st> you <st data-num=\"01792\" class=\"\">crushed</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 03651\">That is why</st> <st data-num=\"06341\" class=\"\">snares</st> <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">surround</st> you,<p class=\"poetry\">and why <st data-num=\"06597\" class=\"\">sudden</st> <st data-num=\"06343\" class=\"\">fear</st> <st data-num=\"0926\" class=\"\">terrifies</st> you,</p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0176\" class=\"\">why</st> it is so <st data-num=\"02822\" class=\"\">dark</st> you <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">cannot</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and why a <st data-num=\"08229\" class=\"\">flood</st><n id=\"2\" /> of <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st> <st data-num=\"03680\" class=\"\">covers</st> you.</p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetrybreak\">\u201cIs <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0433\" class=\"\">God</st> on <st data-num=\"01363\" class=\"\">high</st> in <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">heaven</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">And <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">lofty</st> <st data-num=\"03556\" class=\"\">stars</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">how</st> <st data-num=\"07311\" class=\"\">high</st> they <st data-num=\"07311\" class=\"\">are</st>!</p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">But you have <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> does <st data-num=\"0410\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Does he <st data-num=\"08199\" class=\"\">judge</st> <st data-num=\"01157\" class=\"\">through</st> such <st data-num=\"06205\" class=\"\">deep darkness</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05645\" class=\"\">Thick clouds</st> are a <st data-num=\"05643\" class=\"\">veil</st> for him, so he does <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> us,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">as he <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">goes back and forth</st><p class=\"poetry\">in the <st data-num=\"02329\" class=\"\">vault</st><n id=\"2\" /> of <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">heaven.\u2019</st><n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Will you <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">keep to</st> the <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">old</st> <st data-num=\"0734\" class=\"\">path</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"0205\" class=\"\">evil</st> <st data-num=\"04962\" class=\"\">men</st> have <st data-num=\"01869\" class=\"\">walked</st>\u2014</p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">men<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> were <st data-num=\"07059\" class=\"\">carried off</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">before</st> their <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">time</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">when the <st data-num=\"05104\" class=\"\">flood</st><n id=\"4\" /> was <st data-num=\"03332\" class=\"\">poured out</st><n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">on their <st data-num=\"03247\" class=\"\">foundations</st>?<n id=\"6\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They were <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">saying</st> to <st data-num=\"0410\" class=\"\">God</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">Turn away</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> us,\u2019<p class=\"poetry\">and, \u2018<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> can the <st data-num=\"07706\" class=\"\">Almighty</st> <st data-num=\"06466\" class=\"\">do</st> to us?\u2019<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">But it was <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st><n id=\"1\" /> who <st data-num=\"04390\" class=\"\">filled</st> their <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">houses</st> <p class=\"poetry\">with <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">good</st> things\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">yet the <st data-num=\"06098\" class=\"\">counsel</st> of the <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">wicked</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07368\" class=\"\">was far</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> me.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"06662\" class=\"\">righteous</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> their destruction<n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"08055\" class=\"\">rejoice</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"05355\" class=\"\">innocent</st> <st data-num=\"03932\" class=\"\">mock</st> them <st data-num=\"03932\" class=\"\">scornfully</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> saying,</p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018<st data-num=\"0518 03808\">Surely</st> our <st data-num=\"07009\" class=\"\">enemies</st><n id=\"1\" /> are <st data-num=\"03582\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st> <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">consumes</st> their <st data-num=\"03499\" class=\"\">wealth</st>.\u2019</p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetrybreak\">\u201c<st data-num=\"05532 04994\">Reconcile</st> yourself<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> God,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"07999\" class=\"\">be at peace</st><n id=\"3\" /> with him;<p class=\"poetry\">in this way your <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">prosperity</st> will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">be good</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03947 04994\">Accept</st> <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">instruction</st><n id=\"1\" /> from his <st data-num=\"06310\">mouth</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">store up</st> his <st data-num=\"0561\" class=\"\">words</st><n id=\"2\" /> in your <st data-num=\"03824\" class=\"\">heart</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">If</st> you <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">return</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"07706\" class=\"\">Almighty</st>, you will be <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">built up</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">if you <st data-num=\"07368\" class=\"\">remove</st> <st data-num=\"05766\" class=\"\">wicked behavior</st> <st data-num=\"07368\" class=\"\">far</st> from your <st data-num=\"0168\" class=\"\">tent</st>, </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"07896\" class=\"\">throw</st><n id=\"1\" /> your <st data-num=\"01220\" class=\"\">gold</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">in</st> the <st data-num=\"06083\" class=\"\">dust</st>\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">your gold<n id=\"3\" /> of <st data-num=\"0211\" class=\"\">Ophir</st> <p class=\"poetry\">among the <st data-num=\"06697\" class=\"\">rocks</st> in the <st data-num=\"05158\" class=\"\">ravines</st>\u2014</p>",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">then the <st data-num=\"07706\" class=\"\">Almighty</st> himself will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> your <st data-num=\"01220\" class=\"\">gold</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"08443\" class=\"\">choicest</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st> for you.</p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Surely</st> <st data-num=\"0227\" class=\"\">then</st> you will <st data-num=\"06026\" class=\"\">delight</st> yourself<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">in</st> the <st data-num=\"07706\" class=\"\">Almighty</st><p class=\"poetry\">and will <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">lift up</st> your <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">face</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">toward</st> <st data-num=\"0433\" class=\"\">God</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">You will <st data-num=\"06279\" class=\"\">pray</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> him, and he will <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">hear</st> you,<p class=\"poetry\">and you will <st data-num=\"07999\" class=\"\">fulfill</st> your <st data-num=\"05088\" class=\"\">vows</st> to him.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Whatever you <st data-num=\"01504\" class=\"\">decide on</st><n id=\"1\" /> a <st data-num=\"0562\" class=\"\">matter</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">it will be <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">established</st> for you,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0216\" class=\"\">light</st> will <st data-num=\"05050\" class=\"\">shine</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> your <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">ways</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">When</st> people are <st data-num=\"08213\" class=\"\">brought low</st><n id=\"1\" /> and you <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018<st data-num=\"01466\" class=\"\">Lift</st> them <st data-num=\"01466\" class=\"\">up</st>!\u2019<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">then he will <st data-num=\"03467\" class=\"\">save</st> the <st data-num=\"07807 05869\">downcast</st>;<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">he will <st data-num=\"04422\" class=\"\">deliver</st> even someone who is <st data-num=\"0336\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05355\" class=\"\">innocent</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">who will <st data-num=\"04422\" class=\"\">escape</st><n id=\"2\" /> through the <st data-num=\"01252\" class=\"\">cleanness</st> of your <st data-num=\"03709\" class=\"\">hands</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "30"
  }
]